	rall 8 ticket limit per patron. Patrons exceeding the ticket limit will ha
	ve their orders canceled at the venue's discretion. All sales are final. N
	o refunds or exchanges. Mobile barcodes delayed until 4 days prior to even
	t. Venue reserves the right to change delivery methods. Unless otherwise n
	oted\, each person must have a ticket regardless of age. No babies in arms
	. No Elevator. Ramps only to the balcony level.\nMetal detectors & bag sea
	rch at door. Arrive early. No weapons. www.stgpresents.org/about/safety Th
	is is a general admission event. The ADA section on the seating map does n
	ot represent a specific seat location. When purchasing ADA accessible seat
	ing\, please feel free to contact us by email if assistance is needed with
	 accommodations or companion seating\; you may reach us at accessibility@s
	tgpresents.org. Each accessible seat houses an armless freestanding chair 
	for patrons with mobility impairments and their companions. Please note th
	at our historic theatre has no elevator to the balcony levels.\n\nhttps://
	www.ticketmaster.com/arms-length-theres-a-whole-world-seattle-washington-0
	5-13-2026/event/0F006385CB35AEE3\n\nFrom STG - Neptune Theatre
